2017-02-14T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da4060a687e18cc41e16cbe6dbfab553a630544b","tid":120610,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"奥洲 無文化 歧視"},{"pid":"9be4a68d0c6a73cb139621a593434ae536dfb6da","tid":120610,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英國，韓國，菲律賓<br />\n排名不分先後<br />\n頭兩個係完全冇野好睇<br />\n第三個係因為823慘劇</blockquote><br />\n英國都冇嘢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除咗倫敦同愛丁堡之外真係乜都冇<br />\n去多兩個市睇下發現到到都差唔多<br />\n而且市容治安唔算話好得去邊（雖然意大利同法國直頭慘不忍睹，但起碼佢啲城市都叫做有啲gimmick）<br />\n<br />\n去咗瑞士就覺得瑞士真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔記得寫埋支那添，因為就嚟冇呢個國家嘅概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70570fec9a674e253c281f2fab65114846af7c69","tid":120610,"uid":66540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:02:15.000Z","msg":"中國 - 唔洗講原因喇掛<br />\n菲律賓 - 人質事件<br />\n新加坡 - 悶 悶 同悶"},{"pid":"01ba6d51a0b62bea12d0a82163ce6e32858b2127","tid":120610,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"中國<br />\n<br />\n要數三個地方未必數得出<br />\n不過個人對日本同韓國都冇乜興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd640bbb537f3e647c06124b0aec6c29153d8c7","tid":120610,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"支那<br />\n中國<br />\nChina"},{"pid":"0c770c9f5a7c9f0fa308791415893c8bd7ef6a02","tid":120610,"uid":66714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支那 <br />\n美帝<br />\n菲律賓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有以色列都好憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為成日撩交